query:
UPDATE team_members SET 
  name = 'Georg Blascheck',
  photo = '/team-georg.png',
  role = 'CEO & Founder',
  bio = 'Visionary leader with 15+ years in global real estate investment. Georg has pioneered innovative investment strategies across Asia, Europe, and the Americas.',
  shortBio = 'CEO & Founder with 15+ years in global real estate'
WHERE id = 1;

UPDATE team_members SET 
  name = 'Bibian Pacayra Bock',
  photo = '/team-bibian.png',
  role = 'Chief Investment Officer',
  bio = 'Expert in hospitality investments with deep expertise in Southeast Asian markets. Bibian leads our investment strategy and portfolio management.',
  shortBio = 'CIO with expertise in Southeast Asian hospitality'
WHERE id = 2;

UPDATE team_members SET 
  name = 'Ma. Engela Rose Pacayra Espares',
  photo = '/team-engela.png',
  role = 'Head of Client Relations',
  bio = 'Dedicated to providing exceptional client experiences. Engela ensures seamless communication and personalized service for all our investors.',
  shortBio = 'Head of Client Relations ensuring exceptional service'
WHERE id = 3;

SELECT id, name, role, photo FROM team_members;
